4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT GENERALLY REVISING EDUCATION LAWS TO SUPPORT
5 EARLY LITERACY TARGETED INTERVENTION PROGRAMS; CLARIFYING THE CONDITIONS UNDER
6 WHICH A SCHOOL DISTRICT PARTNERING WITH A COMMUNITY ORGANIZATION IN PROVIDING
7 CLASSROOM-BASED PROGRAMS MAY INCLUDE THOSE CHILDREN IN ENROLLMENT COUNTS FOR
8 ANB PURPOSES; ALLOWING A SCHOOL DISTRICT THAT IS EXPANDING ENROLLMENT IN A
9 CLASSROOM-BASED EARLY LITERACY TARGETED INTERVENTION PROGRAM TO INCREASE ITS ANB
10 COUNT; ESTABLISHING A TEMPORARY EARLY LITERACY TARGETED INTERVENTION BOOST GRANT
11 PROGRAM TO SUPPORT SCHOOL DISTRICTS IN CREATING OR EXPANDING CLASSROOM-BASED
12 EARLY LITERACY TARGETED INTERVENTION PROGRAMS; PROVIDING AN APPROPRIATION;
13 AMENDING SECTIONS 20-9-311, 20-9-313, AND 20-9-516, MCA; AND PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE
14 EFFECTIVE DATE, AN APPLICABILITY DATE, AND A TERMINATION DATE.”
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
